---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="服務價格 | 拓必工作室" description="拓必工作室服務價格清單。提供網站建置、數位業務開發、社群媒體經營與電子報行銷服務，驅動您的 B2B 數位業務成長。">
	<main class="pt-32 pb-20">
		<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
			<!-- Header -->
			<div class="mb-16">
				<h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-black uppercase tracking-tighter mb-4 text-black">Service Pricing</h1>
				<p class="text-xl text-black/60 max-w-2xl font-medium">服務價格：透明的報價與專業的服務，助您驅動數位轉型。</p>
			</div>

			<!-- Pricing Table -->
			<div class="overflow-x-auto shadow-2xl rounded-sm">
				<table class="w-full border-collapse border-t-4 border-black">
					<thead>
						<tr class="bg-black text-white text-left uppercase text-[12px] tracking-[0.2em]">
							<th class="py-6 px-8 font-black border-r border-white/10">服務項目</th>
							<th class="py-6 px-8 font-black border-r border-white/10">價格（台幣）</th>
							<th class="py-6 px-8 font-black">說明</th>
						</tr>
					</thead>
					<tbody class="text-black bg-white">
						<!-- Section: 網站建置服務 -->
						<tr class="bg-[#F3F3F4]">
							<td colspan="3" class="py-4 px-8 font-black text-lg border-b border-black/10">網站建置服務 (Website Construction)</td>
						</tr>
						<tr class="border-b border-black/10 hover:bg-black/5 transition-colors">
							<td class="py-8 px-8">
								<ul class="space-y-3 list-none p-0 m-0">
									<li class="font-black text-lg">1. AI 智能網站診斷服務</li>
									<li class="font-black text-lg">2. 敏捷式網站改版服務</li>
									<li class="pl-6 text-sm font-medium opacity-60">改版企劃 / 網站原型建置</li>
									<li class="font-black text-lg">3. 交付</li>
									<li class="pl-6 text-sm font-medium opacity-60">圖文素材提供 / 網站上線</li>
								</ul>
							</td>
							<td class="py-8 px-8 font-black text-2xl">專案基礎報價</td>
							<td class="py-8 px-8 text-sm font-medium opacity-60 leading-relaxed">依實際需求規模評估。</td>
						</tr>

						<!-- Section: 數位業務開發 -->
						<tr class="bg-[#F3F3F4]">
							<td colspan="3" class="py-4 px-8 font-black text-lg border-b border-black/10">數位業務開發 (Digital Business Development)</td>
						</tr>
						<tr class="border-b border-black/10 hover:bg-black/5 transition-colors">
							<td class="py-8 px-8">
								<div class="font-black text-lg mb-3">1. 社群帳戶啟用 & 電子報系統建置與串接</div>
								<ul class="space-y-2 text-sm font-medium opacity-60 list-disc pl-5 leading-relaxed">
									<li>LinkedIn & Facebook 帳戶設定與啟用</li>
									<li>Company Page Cover 圖檔製作</li>
									<li>第一次 PO 文：圖 + 文 + #hashtags</li>
									<li>電子報系統 (Brevo / Mailerlite / Mailchimp / HubSpot) 設定</li>
									<li>協助 DNS 驗證、Template 1-2 款、首發與名單匯入</li>
								</ul>
							</td>
							<td class="py-8 px-8 font-black text-2xl">$30,000 / 單次</td>
							<td class="py-8 px-8 text-sm font-medium opacity-60 leading-relaxed">
								所有內容均以英文提供，其它語言視需求報價。<br/>
								修改以兩次為限。內容撰寫提供 AI 產生草稿。
							</td>
						</tr>
						<tr class="border-b border-black/10 hover:bg-black/5 transition-colors">
							<td class="py-8 px-8">
								<div class="font-black text-lg mb-3">2. 社群媒體經營 (Social Media for 2B)</div>
								<ul class="space-y-2 text-sm font-medium opacity-60 list-disc pl-5 leading-relaxed">
									<li>每月 4 則 PO 文 (每周一則)</li>
									<li>圖文或影音擇一 (影音含 AI 配音/剪接/字幕)</li>
								</ul>
							</td>
							<td class="py-8 px-8 font-black text-2xl">$20,000 / 每月</td>
							<td class="py-8 px-8 text-sm font-medium opacity-60 leading-relaxed">廠商需提供現有素材。<br>影音需在一分鐘以內。<br>LinkedIn & Facebook 內容同步</td>
						</tr>
						<tr class="border-b border-black/10 hover:bg-black/5 transition-colors">
							<td class="py-8 px-8">
								<div class="font-black text-lg mb-3">3. 電子報行銷 (Newsletter / Direct Email)</div>
								<ul class="space-y-2 text-sm font-medium opacity-60 list-disc pl-5 leading-relaxed">
									<li>內容撰寫、圖片 HTML 排版</li>
									<li>每月維護：2 次發送、A/B 測試、分析報表</li>
								</ul>
							</td>
							<td class="py-8 px-8">
								<div class="font-black text-2xl">$20,000 / 每月</div>
								<div class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wider font-bold opacity-40 mt-3">
									撰寫/排版: $7,000（已有素材）- $8,000（AI 產生素材） / 每則<br/>
									Template: $10,000 / 每次
								</div>
							</td>
							<td class="py-8 px-8 text-sm font-medium opacity-60 leading-relaxed">使用廠商電子報平台。<br>提供 1-2 款 Template 模板選擇。</td>
						</tr>
						<tr class="border-b-2 border-black bg-black/5 font-black hover:bg-black/10 transition-colors">
							<td class="py-10 px-8 text-xl">4. 數位行銷組合 Package :<br><span class="text-sm font-medium opacity-60"> #2 社群媒體經營 + #3 電子報行銷</span></td>
							<td class="py-10 px-8 text-3xl font-black text-black">$30,000 / 每月</td>
							<td class="py-10 px-8">
								<span class="bg-orange-600 text-white px-4 py-2 text-base font-black uppercase tracking-[0.2em]">最佳選擇</span>
							</td>
						</tr>

						<!-- Section: 其它加購價 -->
						<tr class="bg-[#F3F3F4]">
							<td colspan="3" class="py-4 px-8 font-black text-lg border-b border-black/10">其它服務</td>
						</tr>
						<tr class="border-b border-black/10 hover:bg-black/5 transition-colors">
							<td class="py-8 px-8 font-black text-lg">Banner 製作</td>
							<td class="py-8 px-8">
								<div class="font-black text-xl">$1,500 / 每個 <span class="text-xs opacity-40">(已有素材)</span></div>
								<div class="font-black text-xl">$2,500 / 每個 <span class="text-xs opacity-40">(素材 AI 產生)</span></div>
							</td>
							<td class="py-8 px-8 text-sm font-medium opacity-60 leading-relaxed">提供 2 款選擇。</td>
						</tr>
						<tr class="border-b border-black/10 hover:bg-black/5 transition-colors">
							<td class="py-8 px-8 font-black text-lg">單頁 HTML + 圖 網頁製作 <span class="text-xs opacity-40 block mt-1">(不含表單)</span></td>
							<td class="py-8 px-8 font-black text-2xl">$10,000 / 每頁</td>
							<td class="py-8 px-8"></td>
						</tr>
						<tr class="border-b border-black/10 hover:bg-black/5 transition-colors">
							<td class="py-8 px-8 font-black text-lg">Campaign 網頁 <span class="text-xs opacity-40 block mt-1">(含收集 Leads 名單表單)</span></td>
							<td class="py-8 px-8 font-black text-2xl">$20,000 / 每頁</td>
							<td class="py-8 px-8 text-sm font-medium opacity-60 leading-relaxed">使用廠商平台。</td>
						</tr>
						<tr class="border-b border-black/10 hover:bg-black/5 transition-colors">
							<td class="py-8 px-8 font-black text-lg">Video 製作</td>
							<td class="py-8 px-8 font-black text-2xl">專案報價</td>
							<td class="py-8 px-8"></td>
						</tr>
					</tbody>
				</table>
			</div>

			<!-- Contact CTA -->
			<div class="mt-32 p-16 bg-black text-white text-center rounded-sm">
				<h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black mb-8 uppercase tracking-tighter">Ready to Grow Your Business?</h2>
				<p class="text-white/60 mb-12 text-lg font-medium max-w-xl mx-auto">聯絡我們討論您的客製需求！</p>
				<a href="/#contact">
					<button class="bg-white text-black px-12 py-5 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] hover:bg-white/90 hover:scale-[1.05] transition-all duration-300">
						聯絡我們
					</button>
				</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</main>
</Layout>

<style>
	table {
		min-width: 900px;
	}
</style>
